<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0231b01"/><p id="pI01p0231b0101">大齊天統五年歲
<lb ed="C I" n="0231b02"/>次己丑四月<note n="0231001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31071;＝庚【史】</note><app n="0231001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">庚</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31071;</rdg></app>申
<lb ed="C I" n="0231b03"/>朔八日丁卯建</p>
</div2>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c01"/><p id="pI01p0231c0101">蓋若道非真極玄元。言<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">情</unclear>万
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c02"/>類之表。誰有辭城棄位。以布
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c03"/>衣為好者也。若夫芳蓉<note n="0231002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31072;＝姿【史】</note><app n="0231002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">姿</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31072;</rdg></app>婉。
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c04"/>重爵名官。思皆浮庶。仕民□
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c05"/>情貪暮。自不貨身<note n="0231003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01581;＝質【史】</note><app n="0231003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">質</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01581;</rdg></app><note n="0231004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB18861;＝肉【史】</note><app n="0231004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">肉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB18861;</rdg></app>。布<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">髮</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c06"/>淹泥之徒。焉有昏閨闇室。更
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c07"/>續明燈者怖。今都唯那潘景
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c08"/>暉。張煞鬼。李仕暉。陽脩羅。仰
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c09"/>率儒徒七十人等。並雍容雅
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c10"/>素。若孤鵠沖天。綺結<note n="0231005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31073;＝蔥【史】</note><app n="0231005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蔥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31073;</rdg></app>紅。似
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c11"/>群龍集主渚。往曾竹馬餘暇。
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c12"/>縕五禮以俱融。長復脩多。知
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c13"/>四藏而弘解。常願乘風出谷。
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c14"/><note n="0231006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB21570;＝衿【史】</note><app n="0231006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">衿</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB21570;</rdg></app>濟群生。龍宮陃教。昕階大
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c15"/>道。但惕聖之已去。逍迢金山。
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c16"/>薨巔既<note n="0231007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">又＝久【史】</note><app n="0231007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">久</lem><rdg wit="【原】">又</rdg></app>。若不矸彫神狀。想
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c17"/><note n="0231008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30848;＝作【史】</note><app n="0231008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">作</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30848;</rdg></app>當時。<note n="0231009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31173;＝無【史】</note><app n="0231009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">無</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31173;</rdg></app>以紹述嚴議。弘輪
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c18"/>更轉。是以<note n="0231010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30558;＝遠【史】</note><app n="0231010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30558;</rdg></app>詣浮山嶺岫。取
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c19"/>玉類之純貞。還對泉源。礱磨
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c20"/>彫<note n="0231011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB05382;＝琢【史】</note><app n="0231011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">琢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB05382;</rdg></app>。造碑像一<note n="0231012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31074;＝區【史】</note><app n="0231012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">區</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31074;</rdg></app>。二侗菩薩。
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c21"/>北面開光。方侵上頂。因茲妙
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c22"/>瑞。仰諮皇帝。化九夷而同風。
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c23"/><note n="0231013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">棇＝總【史】</note><app n="0231013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">總</lem><rdg wit="【原】">棇</rdg></app>万國以隆強。四王奉<note n="0231014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31075;＝華【史】</note><app n="0231014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">華</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31075;</rdg></app>於
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c24"/>玉珮。諸天貢寶於金葙。<note n="0231015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">逯＝逮【史】</note><app n="0231015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">逮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">逯</rdg></app>及
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c25"/>七祖先零。圓通六道。俱證金<note n="0231016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31076;＝剛【史】</note><app n="0231016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31076;</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c26"/>其辭曰　沖<note n="0231017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08512;＝寂【史】</note><app n="0231017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08512;</rdg></app>妙絕。超越是非。凡
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c27"/>情未達。聖者<note n="0231018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31077;＝能【史】</note><app n="0231018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">能</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31077;</rdg></app>歸。巧存方便。<note n="0231019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04294;＝貿【史】</note><app n="0231019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">貿</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB04294;</rdg></app><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">易</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c28"/><note n="0231020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31078;＝粗【史】</note><app n="0231020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">粗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31078;</rdg></app>衣。<note place="inline">一</note>榮名麗仕。美<note n="0231021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00672;＝豔【史】</note><app n="0231021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">豔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00672;</rdg></app>垂紅。斯皆危
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c29"/>毳。未若真蹤。波論自<note n="0231022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31079;＝鬻【史】</note><app n="0231022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鬻</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31079;</rdg></app>。<note n="0231023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31080;＝嚮【史】</note><app n="0231023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">嚮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31080;</rdg></app>勸鱗空。<note place="inline">二</note>
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c30"/>昏〃六道。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">快</unclear>似深閨。旡人執炬。終墜<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">泥</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c31"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">梨</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">賴</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">茲</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">明</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">哲</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">濟</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">我</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">群</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">迷</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">昔</unclear>兮<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">五</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">色</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">收</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c32"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">在</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">雙</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">林</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">于</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">時</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">還</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">照</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">視</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">我</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">山</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">金</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">脩</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">功</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">練</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">石</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">長</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0231c33"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">去</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">幽</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">沈</unclear>。</p>
